{"tid":1302194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母學生會，你唔代表我","createTime":"2019-07-10T01:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T01:27:36.000Z","uid":191561,"like":19,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a59f86741384eda4ccb56d64d40e39f46f175d5","tid":1302194,"uid":191561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:03:26.000Z","msg":"講左好多次，訴求已經好清晰，傾乜撚？<br />\n<br />\n而且現在係呢個政府管治失效，我地唔認可呢個政府的合法性，佢地係違反基本法而產生既違法政府。<br />\n<br />\n你同個違法政府有乜好傾？"},{"pid":"e9fd9a164b208e298120a140ec5627bcb0f014f6","tid":1302194,"uid":191561,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"係。我地係拒絕同林鄭對話。因為佢地唔係人民認可的政府，佢地係違反基本法而強迫香港人接受的政府。<br />\n<br />\n我地拒絕同違憲違法既政府對話有乜問題？"},{"pid":"88ca5ea6493e2a7cb06edd84aba40087651f6ef0","tid":1302194,"uid":191561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:12:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b88ce287ce922bc4019fd215ed893f95530ac8e6","tid":1302194,"uid":191561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e721abad217d2ead056b791e844631d87fb2f27","tid":1302194,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:14:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bf9ca9b6dd98067e17fa6176fd6abf1b8c4727c9","tid":1302194,"uid":99307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:16:26.000Z","msg":"佢地幾時有話可以代表所有人去傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53472d29507eb68d4ef4679cf4a8ab83e36ad1b4","tid":1302194,"uid":177256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"少啲FF對身體有益。<br />\n大部分人都係反條例、政府態度同班狗過份使用武力，你要拉到咁遠只會一事無成。"},{"pid":"3a176298baa0f3c3782334d5030b2144f6ed03a4","tid":1302194,"uid":247482,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:16:57.000Z","msg":"人地比人擺上檯，已經回得好正路<br />\n<br />\n佢地講左N次自己無代表性, 如林鄭堅持要同無代表性既佢地傾, 都要放哂D人先&quot;考慮&quot;公開傾<br />\n<br />\n你係度打句野屌人就易<br />\